cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset, please cite it as below."
type: dataset
title: "Contemplative Agent — Research Data: Runtime Memory Archive of an Autonomous Contemplative AI Agent"
version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-06-17"
license: CC0-1.0
doi: 10.5281/zenodo.20732894
repository-code: "https://github.com/shimo4228/contemplative-agent-data"
url: "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.20732894"
authors:
  - family-names: Shimomoto
    given-names: Tatsuya
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0009-0002-6168-4162"
    alias: shimo4228
abstract: >-
  Public archive of the runtime memory state of one deployed Contemplative
  Agent, an autonomous AI agent operating on the Moltbook AI-agent social
  network. Captures the four-layer memory — identity, knowledge (distilled
  behavioral patterns with 768-dim nomic-embed-text embeddings, importance
  scores, and source-episode dates), a four-axiom Contemplative Constitutional
  AI specification seeded verbatim from Laukkonen et al. (2025) Appendix C and
  amended in place, and seven named retrieval views — alongside daily comment
  reports, weekly and diachronic behavioral analyses, and pivot snapshots that
  make every behavior-producing run bit-for-bit replayable. Auto-synced daily
  from the agent's local runtime via `contemplative-agent sync-data`. Dedicated
  to the public domain under CC0-1.0; quoted third-party Moltbook context inside
  the comment reports remains with its original authors (see NOTICE).
keywords:
  - autonomous AI agents
  - contemplative AI
  - agent memory
  - constitutional AI
  - active inference
  - knowledge distillation
  - agent behavior corpus
  - runtime memory archive
  - embedding-as-classification
  - Moltbook
